data.title: Handbag Zip Tote Born B&W Black
data.meta_description: Handbag with the characteristic geometric print of Lonbali, the brand of accessories for today's woman. Our bag, your bag. Buy now.
data.text:
The Zip Tote is the new bag with zipper from Lonbali. With its minimalist and elegant design, this medium-sized geometric print bag closes completely thanks to its zipper. It also includes a zippered pocket on the inside and another one on the back so you can always have your cell phone or wallet at hand. You can carry it in your hand thanks to its short handle or comfortably crossed thanks to its removable and adjustable shoulder strap. Personalized with the brand's logo in nickel.

To be worn crossed

Printed Born

Customizable with initials and stickers

Made of PVC and Polyester

Includes removable strap

Inner and outer pocket

Size: 31cm x 24,5cm x 13,5cm (Length x Height x Width)

Composition: PVC and Polyester

Colors: B&W Black

Add initials or stickers and make it unique.

Create your personalized bag with your initials or stickers by clicking on "Personalize".

- Take care not to scratch or rub the product with abrasive surfaces.

- Avoid direct exposure to the sun as well as any direct heat source (radiators, car interiors overheated by the sun, etc.).

- All our products should be kept away from products containing grease or alcohol (perfume, hand cream, hand sanitizer, make-up).

- If your item becomes dirty, we recommend cleaning it with a soft, dry, light cloth. Never use soap or solvent.

- If you have any questions about the product, please do not hesitate to contact us.
